        ["ExecuteAsync calling QueueDeclareAsync for \u201cemployee.events.Queue\u201d", "The ReceiveEndpoint(\u201cemployee.events.Queue\u201d, ...) configuration in Program.cs (Step 5) declares and binds the queue"],
        ["AsyncEventingBasicConsumer + ReceivedAsync event handler", "The single Consume(ConsumeContext&lt;EmployeeEvent&gt;) method &mdash; MassTransit dispatches to it per message"],
        ["Encoding.UTF8.GetString(...) + JsonSerializer.Deserialize<...>", "context.Message is already a deserialized, strongly-typed EmployeeEvent"],
        ["await _channel.BasicAckAsync(eventArgs.DeliveryTag, false)", "Automatic: MassTransit acknowledges the message when Consume returns without throwing"],
        ["StopAsync closing _channel / _connection", "Automatic: the MassTransit hosted service closes the shared bus connection on shutdown"],
